('24', '1', 'ABOUT US', '', 'Founded in 1997, Viking cruises has been committed to the applied research and practical operation of cultural tourism development for many years. Adhering to the values of content innovation, the integration of knowledge and practice, based on the local ', '\n&lt;h3&gt;Company profile&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Founded in 1997, Viking cruises has been committed to the applied research and practical operation of cultural tourism development for many years. Adhering to the values of content innovation, the integration of knowledge and practice, based on the local Chinese culture and integrated with the international advanced concepts, Viking cruises has established the whole industry chain research and development and service system of tourism destinations. After 20 years of development, landscape has developed into a comprehensive tourism destination construction service organization covering five business areas: planning and design, tourism investment, destination development, smart tourism and cultural tourism construction.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Viking ship brave frontier in the field of tourism and its extension, professor in international tourism research institute academician wu will tiger to chief scientist, in a professional, dedicated and professional SanYe spirit as the core cultural value, to &quot;reserved for the earth and the creation of beautiful scenery&quot; for the mission, condensed the world\'s top intelligence resources, and grasp the domestic and foreign tourism industry development trend, best strategic resources and supply chain integration of upstream and downstream industry brand, tailor systematic solution according to customer\'s actual needs, for the society, create and share special value for customers, for employees.&lt;/p&gt;\n', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'page', '1558942317', '1558942687', '1558942260', '24', '1', '{\"thumbnail\":\"cms\\/20190527\\/bb0a049945974e8070a8df7760e967a6.png\"}'),
